        INNER JOIN [Permissions] AS [p] ON [f].[Id] = [p].[FunctionId]
        INNER JOIN [AppRoles] AS [r] ON [p].[RoleId] = [r].[Id]
        WHERE ([r].[Name] IN (N'Staff', N'Customer', N'Admin', N'Quản trị viên') AND ([f].[Id] = @__functionId_1)) AND ([p].[CanDelete] = 1))

END" (0723d8ff)
